WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.240
CHAPTERS III AND IV of I Corinthians.

00:05.240 --> 00:14.240
This is a LibriVox recording. All LibriVox recordings are in the public domain.

00:14.760 --> 00:21.800
